    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前所未有的幻想世界！现邀请大家去探索埋藏在古代查库鲁文明遗址深处里的谜团，快来游玩这</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >款经典且史诗般的3D平台冒险游戏《露娜&amp;查库鲁传奇》吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏结合了动作元素和多个可探索区域，使得玩家沉浸在一个既引人入胜又充满黑暗色彩的</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事中。面对“公司”隐藏的谜团，玩家需要解开这些有趣的各种谜题，并且玩法适合全家一起享</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/690aefb326b09f67104d5a7b09db25d5.poster.avif?t=1769005232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/690aefb326b09f67104d5a7b09db25d5.webm?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/690aefb326b09f67104d5a7b09db25d5.mp4?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不可错过的精彩故事！沉浸在赤红大陆，玩家将会通过了解神秘的查库鲁文明并揭开其所有的古</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老秘密。玩家需要扮演勇敢无畏的露娜，直面各种试图使得任务复杂化的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/2227ff5583ece06af81bb2e93ec00d09.poster.avif?t=1769005232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/2227ff5583ece06af81bb2e93ec00d09.webm?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/2227ff5583ece06af81bb2e93ec00d09.mp4?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>3D平台</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备踏上一次充满刺激和挑战的难忘冒险吧，这款令人惊叹不已的3D平台游戏专为Steam上</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >的经典电子游戏爱好者所设计！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/de01247eda62277e909a860ed0094347.poster.avif?t=1769005232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/de01247eda62277e909a860ed0094347.webm?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/de01247eda62277e909a860ed0094347.mp4?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个不为人知的广阔而梦幻般的世界！游戏场景受拉丁美洲美丽风景和文化的启发，玩家可</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以根据自己的节奏探索里面不同的景观，无论是想收集所有物品还是寻找解决挑战的方法，都由</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家自己决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/49ad9ebee195d0e2836649f89bf5ce37.poster.avif?t=1769005232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/49ad9ebee195d0e2836649f89bf5ce37.webm?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283470/extras/49ad9ebee195d0e2836649f89bf5ce37.mp4?t=1769005232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>特点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 结合动作和探索元素以及自动视角移动的经典3D冒险平台游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 加入到好奇心旺盛且勇敢无畏的冒险者露娜的冒险旅途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 在这片赤红大陆上揭露古代查库鲁文明以及四种神秘种子的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 探索这片有着废墟、丛林、河流、瀑布、洞穴等不同地貌的壮丽世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 掌握流星锤的用法，与各式各样的奇妙敌人战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 克服3D平台障碍并解开查库鲁留下的谜题以守护该文明的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 解锁神秘技能来改变环境并抵达新的场地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 收集古代世界的年代久远且古怪的文物。</p>",
